# Todays Coffee With News -- Setup Guide

Ye automation din mein **4 baar** (6 AM, 10 AM, 5 PM, 8 PM IST) Instagram
pe news carousel post karta hai aur Telegram pe notification bhejta hai.

## Kya karta hai
1. NewsAPI.org se India ke top headlines fetch karta hai
2. Pehle se post hui headlines skip karta hai (duplicate avoid)
3. Har headline ko Claude (Anthropic API) se Hinglish mein translate karta hai
4. Unsplash se headline-related background image leta hai
5. Har headline ka ek carousel slide (PNG) banata hai
6. Instagram pe carousel post karta hai
7. Telegram pe "post upload ho gaya" notification bhejta hai

## Step 1 -- Naye Facebook Page se Instagram connect karo

1. Naya Facebook Page already bana hua hai ("Todays Coffee With News")
2. Confirm karo Instagram professional account isse linked hai (Instagram
   app > Settings > Account > Linked accounts)
3. [Graph API Explorer](https://developers.facebook.com/tools/explorer/) khol
4. App select karo, "Get User Access Token" pe ye permissions tick karo:
   `instagram_basic`, `instagram_content_publish`, `pages_show_list`,
   `pages_read_engagement`, `business_management`
5. `GET /me/accounts` chalao -> Page ID milega
6. `GET /{page-id}?fields=instagram_business_account` chalao -> IG_USER_ID milega

## Step 2 -- Long-lived token banao

Short-lived token ko long-lived mein convert karo:
```
GET https://graph.facebook.com/v23.0/oauth/access_token?
  grant_type=fb_exchange_token&
  client_id={app-id}&
  client_secret={app-secret}&
  fb_exchange_token={short-lived-token}
```
Jo `access_token` milega wahi `NEWS_IG_ACCESS_TOKEN` hai.

## Step 3 -- NewsAPI key lo

1. [newsapi.org](https://newsapi.org) pe free account banao
2. Dashboard se API key copy karo -> `NEWS_API_KEY`

## Step 4 -- Unsplash key lo

1. [unsplash.com/developers](https://unsplash.com/developers) pe app banao
2. "Access Key" copy karo -> `UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY`

## Step 5 -- Anthropic (Claude) API key lo

1. [console.anthropic.com](https://console.anthropic.com) pe account banao
2. Billing set karo (chhota sa cost lagega per-request, paise mein fraction)
3. API key generate karo -> `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`

## Step 6 -- Telegram bot details

Agar quotes wale automation mein already bot bana hai, **same bot reuse**
kar sakte ho:
- `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` -- wahi jo pehle se hai
- `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` -- wahi jo pehle se hai

## Step 7 -- GitHub repo banao aur Secrets add karo

1. Naya **private** repo banao (jaise `news-auto-poster`)
2. Saari files isme upload karo (fonts folder bhi -- drag & drop se,
   "choose your files" link se nahi)
3. Repo > Settings > Secrets and variables > Actions > "New repository secret"
   -- ye 6 secrets add karo:
   - `NEWS_IG_USER_ID`
   - `NEWS_IG_ACCESS_TOKEN`
   - `NEWS_API_KEY`
   - `UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY`
   - `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`
   - `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN`
   - `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID`

## Step 8 -- Workflow enable karo aur test karo

1. Repo > Actions tab > "Daily News Post" workflow > "Enable workflow"
   (agar pehli baar hai to ye option dikhega)
2. "Run workflow" button se manually ek baar trigger karo (testing ke liye,
   bina 6 AM tak wait kiye)
3. Logs check karo agar koi error aaye

## Token maintenance

`NEWS_IG_ACCESS_TOKEN` roughly 60 din mein expire hota hai. Quotes wale
automation jaisa hi, isko bhi periodically refresh karna hoga (manually
ya `refresh_token.py` jaisa script add karke automate kar sakte ho).

## Schedule (already set hai)

| IST Time | UTC (cron) |
|----------|-----------|
| 6:00 AM  | 00:30 |
| 10:00 AM | 04:30 |
| 5:00 PM  | 11:30 |
| 8:00 PM  | 14:30 |

Workflow file: `.github/workflows/daily-news-post.yml`
